{
  "stem": "6989.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we went to stay with her, because we felt that that would be safe since there are no neighbors-- or at least immediate neighbors.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For me, it was forever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't remember ever being without her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know what year they were married or when they had my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was probably 13 or 12 at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I would say at least 12 or 15 years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this point-- you know, looking at the picture that I have of her-- I don't think she was more than like 30 or 35.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was never married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her whole life was devoted to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite-- it was a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- you know, I guess like maybe a room and a half.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe two rooms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, the main room was always with a big table and with this oven that I described to you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The farm itself in that place I do not remember, because as I said, I was not there that long.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was hidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was not exposed out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So how could I know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No other children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, her mother-- you know, it's funny because she had like very big skirts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Several of them, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have a picture in my mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She always brought me something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she would pick up like several layers of skirts, and whatever it was-- whether it was candy, or nuts, or whatever-- would be in her-- in one of her skirt's pockets.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she would hand me candy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were farmers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think big farmers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never was in that village, because I was hidden.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
